<!-- DISPATCH -->
<section class="dispatch">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="dispatch-box">
      <h3>What is this, exactly?</h3>
      <p>
        cheetochopsticks is a civic data project built by two residents of Colorado Springs —
        <strong>StorySeed Studios and The Dais</strong> — at a kitchen table, with public records,
        too much coffee, and a sincere belief that people who live somewhere
        deserve to actually understand it.
      </p>
      <p>
        Everything here is free. No paywall, no pitch deck, no monetization strategy.
        <strong>No invoice attached.</strong> If it helps one person ask a better question
